Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If your blood type is B, you should be extra cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If left unchecked, things can degrade even further,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to the point where your very life is at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No shows about being sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to be that scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to die, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying? You're only six!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We really need to find another nursery soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The huge companies that all of the smart guys work at...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...are supposed to have their own daycare services and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But where on Earth does that actually happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kawachi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi-san, did you meet someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been heading home pretty early recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You always used to be on the last train home, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year you clocked up some pretty huge profits for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just because I worked my ass off last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't expect those kinds of figures all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes and goes. They don't call me "Daikichi" for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.46,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: In Japanese, "Daikichi" means "great fortune".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to the fourth floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Are you doing as well as ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so much this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've just been getting chewed out by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm losing my hair over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do a good job once, and you set the bar really high for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Gotou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't act so surprised just because I'm small!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that you're pretty thin. I was\Nwondering where you could've fit a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your guess is as good as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid's already two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Put it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotou-san's just as tough as always, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame she didn't stay in sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been with the company a few years longer than I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And when she got pregnant, she willingly requested a demotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that she'd be able to make it home on time every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The office was full of gossip about what she had done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! How long are you keeping her for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't really decided yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rin-chan", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going through a bed-wetting phase right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It really seems to be getting to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's psychological?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, though kids sweat a whole lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the winter and autumn, that doesn't happen as much,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so they start needing to pee a lot more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always told to use the toilet before bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess her mother must have had a lot on her plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to ask her, even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really important for a kid to have a mother, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Men aren't supposed to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you up to today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture books, staring contests and other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, I'll whip up dinner right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon's fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Why are you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that you didn't want to get dragged into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't very well stay out of it when I know she's with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading there for the weekend to look for clues about Rin's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Then call when the two of you arrive at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure she gets wrapped up in something warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, and I'll call Haruko, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Her kid and Rin seem to get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, another car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan, good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't really have anything a young child would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to like old people's food, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Had enough already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come and tell me that you're hungry later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not very hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for leaving leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that damn family!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan! You actually took her home!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we'll see warm sunlight all across the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...with reported temperatures two degrees higher than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.86,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to use the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go when you're sitting right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. At my place, she talks a lot more than you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the train, she was acting like she was on holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we turned up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,she found an old couple from the funeral who scared her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you trying to accuse us of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! When she sees adults in a bad mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,she thinks that they're mad at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I suppose a child would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the two of you were the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Even an insensitive blockhead like you had a heart, once upon a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Rin just has her head screwed on a little better than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it, baldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan, you like cat's cradle, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, at least answer her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch how Auntie does it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Auntie"? You're more like her grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not old enough to be a grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely child...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just because she grew up with {\i1}really{\i0} old people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how to do it, so watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My... Did I make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This? A four-step ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A two-step.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,An aeroplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because this cord is so easy to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I knitted it out of thin wool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a much better weight than if you use the thread as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's good with her hands, so we can teach her otedama, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.38,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: Otedama is a Japanese children's game involving juggled beanbags.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You take your pinkie, and thread it through here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One for a rattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Two for a wisteria tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this? What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I could ask the same about what you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably Haruko and her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty! What are they called?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Otedama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's kind of amazing that you're juggling a job and raising a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband hardly helps out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to your granddad's after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I figured there might be some clues about Rin's mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely think it's important for a child to have her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've at least left a will or something, Granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you worried about Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A modem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that on your head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina-chan did my hair like hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, now that you mention it, your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Kazumi-oneechan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kazumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, you can't dress a kid up in old junk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I knew they'd suit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I guess it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put them on a kid today, they actually look kind of modern...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything at your grandfather's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I suppose it's best not to get\Nworked up and press Rin-chan for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we never told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but your mother kept working even after you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wasn't she always a housewife?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When she was pregnant with Kazumi, she pushed herself too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and ended up in the hospital for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time she returned to work, she had been all but pushed out of her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother was terribly upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kazumi was a newborn, and so tiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...that your mother often had to take time off of work or come home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kazumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother put so much effort into raising Kazumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...that she ended up like she is now, as loud and rambunctious as they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Do you want Dad to drive you to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. We'll get there on time even if we walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked if we can come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie will be waiting, so come by whenever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it'd be nice to give us a grandchild?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I could look after the baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep working and raise a child at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so the woman {\i1}always{\i0} loses out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I still want to wear swimsuits, go drinking and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rin. Was there a computer at Granddad's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what a computer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Granddad use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The maid used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What sort of person was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate Masako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She hated me, and she always got mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She was scary, so I forgot all about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit late to be saying this, but it's tough trying to juggle a job and raise a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is. Not a moment's peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotou-san, have you ever felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...you've sacrificed yourself for your child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean when I was demoted at the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I know it's rude of me to ask, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at the time, I thought it was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything turned out okay, so why worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if I felt that way, I'd never come out and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't underestimate the power of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... "Kotodama", was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.01,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: "Kotodama" is an ancient Japanese belief that words and names possess mystical or supernatural power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that answer too abstract?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I understand completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll teach me lots more about children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! But your kid's much older than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be teaching me, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin... You should've just woken me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But... It's sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what it is. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it like to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to die before me, Daikichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadness over Granddad passing away,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,anxiety over what she'd do if I died...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...and her own fear of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So many things she couldn't sort out, all jumbled in the back of her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about that until you're a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When will I be a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No... You don't need to worry about it until you're an old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't worry about wetting the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you use the toilet before bedtime, and you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But going to the toilet is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if you wet the bed, you just need to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to get mad about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing to laugh at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to call you out on such short notice, Hiraka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to sound sudden, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please transfer me to a department where I won't be doing overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Kawachi, are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Deadly serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's what's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I think it's extremely disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have children, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try and put in a good word to the head of the department.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Thank you for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But your subordinates aren't going to be pleased...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have asked another relative or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably shouldn't tell him that I took her in on the heat of the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, aren't there nurseries that watch children until late at night?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to work under anyone except you, Kawachi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but the higher-ups shuffle around the company's hierarchy a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in getting worked up about it every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Things will settle down in my department without me, eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be able to deal with a little reshuffling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be weird if an organisation couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rin is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I'm right to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. This much rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Towel, lunchbox, indoor shoes, toothbrush, cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We've put your name on them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! A futon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. That's for the infants' class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'd be lying through my teeth\Nif I said that I wasn't sacrificing something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hope that several years down the line, I'll be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Rin, that thing you have on your handtowel and lunchbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... The dog thing with the long ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lop-eared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lop... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not a spotty dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, go to the toilet first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to keep dreaming forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to be kinder?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't continue it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Rin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now I'm training for the sports meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.66,0:23:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I got much better at dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, or the time after that, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The next story is "Letter".
